Interface HwResource

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface HwResource
extends Resource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Description
    • Frequency
    • End Points
    • PHW Services
    • RHW Services
    • Owned HW
    See Also:
    HwGeneralPackage.getHwResource()
